FORTNITE_GIFT_INVENTORY_INFO: Get your gear to match your
Discord Drop by doing one of two things:
Stream live and Screen Share Fortnite on Discord for 15+ or more minutes to at least one Discord friend.
After 15 minutes of screen sharing to a friend, you’ll receive a link as a gift in your Settings
Click the link to log into your Epic Games account and the Wrap will be added to your Fortnite Locker!
Can’t stream? You can also accept the Discord Bot Quest! Start by joining the
In the server, you’ll see a bot you can interact with to join the Discord Quest.
Upon interacting with the bot, you’ll be taken to a page where you can link your Epic and Discord accounts.
With your accounts linked, participate in the Quest by completing a task inside Discord and a task inside Fortnite.
After both of these tasks are complete, the Wrap will be added to your Fortnite Locker!
Learn more on our blog post!
